	<div class= "container">
	<div class= "section">
		<div class= "row">
			<div class ="col s8"><%= image_tag "tour/i1.jpg", class:"responsive-img" %></div>
			<div class ="col s4"><h5>Setting up <b>your shop</b> is very easy! Just browse to the <b>My Shop</b> tab in your dashboard...</h5></div>
		</div>
		  <div class= "divider"></div><br><br>
		<div class= "row">
			<div class ="col s8"><%= image_tag "tour/i2.jpg" , class:"responsive-img" %></div>
			<div class ="col s4"><br><br><br><h5>Add a <b>description</b>...</h5></div>
		</div>
		  <div class= "divider"></div><br><br>
		<div class= "row">
			<div class ="col s8"><%= image_tag "tour/i3.jpg" , class:"responsive-img" %></div>
			<div class ="col s4"><h5>And simply <b>configure</b> your commission slots! Unless you're a <b>Pro</b> account, you'll be able to create only <b>three</b> (if you are, the number is unlimited!). </h5></div>
		</div>		
		  <div class= "divider"></div><br><br>
		<div class= "row">
			<div class ="col s8"><%= image_tag "tour/i4.jpg" , class:"responsive-img" %></div>
			<div class ="col s4"><h5>You'll be able to configure the <b>number of slots</b> available, the <b>time</b> you estimate it's going to take and the <B>price</b> for each type of commission (or service) you advertise on your shop.</h5></div>
		</div>
		  <div class= "divider"></div><br><br>
		<div class= "row">
			<div class ="col s8"><%= image_tag "tour/i5.jpg" , class:"responsive-img" %></div>
			<div class ="col s4"><h5>Your shop's gonna look as awesome as Wayne's when you're done...</h5></div>
		</div>		
		  <div class= "divider"></div><br><br>
		<div class= "row">
			<div class ="col s8"><%= image_tag "tour/i6.jpg" , class:"responsive-img" %></div>
			<div class ="col s4"><h5>And if a <b>client</b> happens to ask for a commission, he's going to have the option to go <%= link_to "secure", "#explain" , class:"modal-trigger" %> or not. In any case, we'll forward you an email.</h5></div>
		</div>
	</div>
	</div>
	

<div id="explain" class="modal">
		<div class="modal-content" align="center">
			A secure transaction means that the request will
			be handled through the site. We will give you an ID so you can check on the progress
			of your commission, and we'll withhold the payment to the artist until you've indicated
			that it's completed. Should anything happen, we will reimburse you. There's a transaction fee of 8%. 
		</div>
		<div class="modal-footer">
			<a href="#!" class="modal-action modal-close waves-effect waves-green btn-flat">Close</a>
		</div>
	</div>